{"about_the_game":"The world as you know it no longer exists: black clouds hover over the planet, strange shadows lurk everywhere.<br>The only solution? Explore the lost continent.<br><br>In this FPS metroidvania, you need to master the art of bubbles.<br>Shoot bubbles on elemental foes, use the best element to deal maximum damage.<br>Unlock platforming abilities used by shooting lasers at your bubbles allowing you to reach unreachable places.<br>For example:<br>Earth bubbles allow you to create platforms:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507670/extras/EarthSphereJump.gif?t=1697199832\" /><br>Water bubbles make you jump higher:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507670/extras/WaterSphereJump.gif?t=1697199832\" /><br>Wind bubbles make you jump further:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507670/extras/WindSphereJump.gif?t=1697199832\" /><br><br>Use these at your advantage during fight. Or simply craft and use powerful potions.<br><br>To progress in you exploration you also need to solve bubble physics based puzzles.<br><br>Put the pieces together to find the cause of the blight and a way to cure it!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1697199832","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507670/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1697199832","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507670/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1697199832","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507670/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1697199832","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"The